==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Non-feasance
<hw>Non-fea"sance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>non-</ets> + OF. <ets>faisance</ets> a doing, fr. <ets>faire</ets>
to do.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>An omission or neglect to do
something, esp. that which ought to have been done. Cf.
<er>Malfeasance</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>non-finite</ent>⟦br⟧
